@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <hr />

    <p>
        This application was developed as part of the module
        <strong>Modern Programming Principles and Practice</strong>.
        It is a student project created for educational purposes.
    </p>

    <h4>Data Collection</h4>
    <p>
        The system stores basic information required to manage the community library,
        including book records, member information, and loan records.
    </p>

    <h4>Member Information</h4>
    <p>
        Member data such as name, email address, and phone number is used only
        for managing library memberships and tracking borrowed books.
    </p>

    <h4>Data Usage</h4>
    <p>
        All stored information is used exclusively within this application
        to support the management of books, members, and loans.
    </p>

    <h4>Educational Use</h4>
    <p>
        This system is not intended for production use and does not collect
        real personal data. Any data used in this system may be generated
        using fake data tools for testing and demonstration purposes.
    </p>

</div>
